{"tid":1563726,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"文書剪片laptop  求推介","createTime":"2019-09-12T13:31:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T17:07:04.000Z","uid":170301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"897c7f2f9d8406f4a3410cad4892c93639f41ffe","tid":1563726,"uid":170301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:31:53.000Z","msg":"Budget:  ~10k<br />\n<br />\n要求 (排名分先後) ：<br />\n1. 輕身，方便攜帶<br />\n2. Keyboard 好打 (經常打字) <br />\n3. 大電量 (用到&gt;10 hours)<br />\n4. 適合剪片 (要求唔高，片段20分鐘內，1080p)<br />\n5. 最少8GB RAM, 256GB storage<br />\n<br />\n自己本身用緊Thinkpad (唔係 X1 carbon), 機身重同埋電開始消耗得快。<br />\n<br />\n有考慮/聽過 (不分先後):  <br />\n1. Macbook air <br />\n2. Macbook pro <br />\n3. Thinkpad X1 Carbon <br />\n4. Dell XPS 13 <br />\n5. Acer Swift 5<br />\n6. Asus Zenbook 13&quot;/14&quot;<br />\n7. 其他建議<br />\n<br />\n請問以上laptop 值唔值得買，同埋佢地價錢點樣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n頭3個options 可能有d overbudget. 有冇d laptop 冇咁貴又滿足到我要求架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁多位ching 有咩建議俾小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"740688ba5f876fd39a1ad822ecb88b2e694454d2","tid":1563726,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:32:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.